reviewText: Greatest performer in the world huge fan of Celine

nice to see glimpse into celines humor..the road she is on during tour..the ins out of a show.behind scenes..and enough music to enjoy that fabulous voice..not a typical concert dvd..didn't aspect on it.well worth it..very enjoyable
